https://shalabh.com/programmable-systems/offload-mental-simulation.html

A live programming UI with tools and language support for offloading the work
of mentally executing the program to understand how it works.
(Not a concrete design; it's more a set of requirements.)

* What if this variable has that value? Show me an abstract execution trace.
  Branches not taken are greyed out.
* Interactive 'program slicing' (wikipedia).
